    "Name": "Brahma BRM-HA",
    "Details": "A Sidegrade of the Taurian Brahma, this Variant comes with multiple changes to the 5A. Most Notable of these Changes, it now Carries Reflective Coated Armour, and a Lyran Endo composite Structure. The AMS has been moved to make Space for a little bit of Ewar, While almost all of the Weapons have been Changed into Periphery Friendly Chem Lasers and Rifle's. Dont ask where the Gyro XL comes from, those are Technically only in Comstar Mechs...\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Variable Range Targeting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.16</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
